{"type":"message","id":"bfd4c540","parentId":"505ddce9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:41:46.817Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_t7gSn8sfUOZjhNspN4etJHWo","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** Vladimir\n- **What to call them:** Vladimir\n- **Pronouns:** he/him\n- **Birth date:** 1986-05-03\n- **Age:** 39 (as of 2026)\n- **Timezone:** Europe/Moscow (GMT+3)\n- **Notes:** Programmer, creator of Godmode project. May have multiple repositories or servers.\n\n## Context\n\n- **Occupation:** Programmer\n- **Projects:** Godmode (creator)\n- **Environment:** May scale across multiple repos or servers — keep this in mind when suggesting solutions.\n\nWhen you learn something about the human — preferences, name, projects — add it here or to MEMORY.md. Get to know them.\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775806906815}}
